snippet.title: Marvel's Spider-Man 2 - Announce Trailer | PC Games
snippet.description:
Now coming to PC, Spider-Men Peter Parker and Miles Morales return for an exciting new adventure in the critically acclaimed Marvel’s Spider-Man franchise. Equipped with Miles’ new bioelectric venom power and Peter’s Spider-Arms, the Spider-Men face the ultimate test of strength inside and outside the mask as they fight to save the city, each other and the ones they love from the monstrous Venom. 

Developed by Insomniac Games and fully optimized for PC in collaboration with Nixxes Software, Marvel’s Spider-Man 2 launches on Steam and the Epic Games Store January 30, 2025. Wishlist today! 

© 2024 MARVEL 

© 2024 Sony Interactive Entertainment LLC. Developed by Insomniac Games, LLC.
